Class InstanceHandler.ManagedConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.composite.instance.InstanceHandler.ManagedConfiguration
  • Enclosing class:
    InstanceHandler

    class InstanceHandler.ManagedConfiguration
extends Object
    This structure aims to manage a configuration. It stores all necessary information to create an instance and to track the factory.
